<br>
1) When I'm not pulling, I hit taunt, kick, disarm, auto-attack to drag the mob off the puller<br>
2) I keep other's spells set to group, so I get messages when tash/slow/snare land.  I'll hit taunt immediately after one of these lands<br>
3) When the mob turns on a group member, I hit taunt.<br>
4) When the mob enrages, I hit taunt &amp; disarm for the duration of the enrage.<br>
