<br>
I taunt when mob turns<br>
I taunt when a large heal is caste.<br>
I taunt when mob agro's on chanter or nuker.<br>
I taunt constantly when Rogue is present.<br>
I also set my /shield with the healers name<br>
I also set a /shield %T in case of other agro<br>
I use disarm very sporatically, unless a weapon is present.<br>
<br>
I also found that if Taunt is not working well, for whatever reason, a timed Taunt/kick works almost every time.  I donno if I'm just trippin or if it actually works, but it appears to.<br>
<br>
I'm not sure if this is the most efficient way or not, but it appears to work really well for me...of course I'm only 38 and any advice/suggestions are always accepted.<br>
