<br>
Because of the time between your random press of the taunt button and when you might actually *need* that taunt. Some caster is bound to land some high aggro spell the moment after you pop the taunt button. The caster is then tanking the mob until your taunt button refreshes.<br>
<br>
Having said that, yes, sometimes I'm a masher too. <p><A href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=140750><img border="0" src="http://mywebpages.comcast.net/bdiebold5/tugedit.jpg"></A></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showMessageRange?topicID=2691.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a> <b>2</b> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showMessageRange?topicID=2691.topic&start=41&stop=60>3</a><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showMessageRange?topicID=2691.topic&start=61&stop=80>4</a><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showMessageRange?topicID=2691.topic&start=81&stop=100>5</a><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showMessageRange?topicID=2691.topic&start=101&stop=120>6</a><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showMessageRange?topicID=2691.topic&start=121&stop=134>7</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showPrevMessage?topicID=2691.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showNextMessage?topicID=2691.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.emailToFriend?topicID=2691.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.threadControl?topicID=2691.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=2691.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies